      "url": "https://ttandmore.com/es/terms-and-conditions/",
      "content": "Terms and Conditions | TT & More\n+52 (998) 300 0307\nENES\nDestinos\nServices Shuttle AeropuertoHotel a HotelGrupos\nTours Chichén Itzá ExpressTulum Express\nContactoo\nReservar\nInicioShuttle AeropuertoToursContactoo\nTérminos y Condiciones\nPlease read the following terms before booking your service.\nTransportation Terms and Conditions\nThese policies apply to both arrivals and departure transfers, as well as shuttle, tour, and group services offered by TT & More.\n1. Reservation Process\nVia our website, WhatsApp, or email, you may book our service by providing the following information: Name of the guest or lead passenger, number of passengers, date and time of the service, flight information, and hotel name.\nChildren under 2 years old travel free and do not count toward the passenger total. Children ages 2 and older are counted as passengers.\n2. Payment Terms\nOur prices are listed in US Dollars (USD). Payment can be made via PayPal, Mercado Pago, or cash in USD or MXN at the prevailing exchange rate.\nFull prepayment is required to confirm your reservation.\n3. Cancellation Policy\nYou may cancel your reservation at least 24 hours before the scheduled service with a 7% fee for banking charges.\nNo refunds will be issued for cancellations made less than 24 hours before the scheduled service.\nNo-shows are non-refundable.\n4. Flight Monitoring\nIt is very important that you notify us of any changes to your flight. Our staff will be monitoring your flight and will be waiting for you upon arrival. However, if your flight info changes and we are not notified, we cannot guarantee on-time pickup.\n5. Vehicle Types\nOur fleet includes: Toyota Hiace, Nissan Urvan (up to 10 passengers), Toyota Sienna, and Toyota Highlander (up to 4 passengers with limited luggage). Vehicle assignment is based on group size and availability.\n6. Additional Stops\nStops are allowed with prior notice. For a stop of up to 1 hour, our fee is $30 USD. Please inform us after making your reservation if you will need to make a stop.\n7. Car Seats\nWe can provide car seats upon request. However, our staff is not authorized to install them; installation must be done by the client due to insurance regulations.\n8. Pets\nWe are pet-friendly! We can transport domestic pets as long as they are in their carriers, and the carrier must fit within the vehicle.\n9. Luggage\nStandard luggage is included. Please notify us in advance if you have oversized luggage, surfboards, golf bags, or other special items so we can assign the appropriate vehicle.\n10. Liability\nTT & More provides fully insured transportation. Our liability is limited to the transportation service contracted. We are not responsible for delays caused by traffic, weather, road conditions, or other events beyond our control.\n11. Currency\nAll prices listed on our website are in USD. Payments in MXN are accepted at the prevailing exchange rate on the day of service.\n12. Contacto\nFor questions about these terms, please contact:\nEmail: contact@ttandmore.com\nWhatsApp: +52 (998) 300 0307\nLast updated: January 2026\nTransporte seguro y confiable del Aeropuerto de Cancún desde 1993.\nEnlaces Rápidos\nInicio\nShuttle Aeropuerto\nHotel a Hotel\nGrupos\nTours\nChichén Itzá Express\nTulum Express\nContactoo\n📞 +52 (998) 300 0307\n📧 contact@ttandmore.com\n📧 bookings@ttandmore.com\n&copy; 2026 TT & More.\nTerms\nConserje IA TT & More\nEn línea — Listo para ayudar\nBienvenido a TT & More. Soy su conserje digital personal. Ya sea que necesite un traslado exclusivo al aeropuerto o un tour privado por la Riviera Maya, estoy aquí para asistirle. ¿Cómo puedo hacer que su viaje sea excepcional hoy?\nTarifas\nReservar Traslado\nExplorar Tours\nServicios para Grupos\nPowered by JegoDigital AI"
